OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly dry start, with some
OL,6,Fearly sunny spells. However, cloud
OL,7,Fsoon thickening from the west, with
OL,8,Fwinds also strengthening. Rain and
OL,9,Fdrizzle then moving into the
OL,10,Fnorthwest, with hill fog, before
OL,11,Fspreading further east. Some
OL,12,Fsoutheastern parts staying dry
OL,13,Fthroughout.
OL,14,
OL,15,CTonight:FRain and drizzle will become
OL,16,Fwidespread through the evening, mostly
OL,17,Flight but with some heavier bursts
OL,18,Fpossible. Maybe the odd drier spell
OL,19,Fdeveloping towards dawn. Winds also
OL,20,Feasing. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,168,160,301,260,100,100
