OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FOutbreaks of mostly light rain
OL,6,Fand drizzle slowly easing, with drier
OL,7,Fintervals developing. Staying cloudy
OL,8,Ffor most, but perhaps the odd brighter
OL,9,For sunny spell in the south later.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,12,Fwith rain Saturday morning, clearing
OL,13,Fto brighter spells. Winds
OL,14,Fstrengthening Sunday, but otherwise
OL,15,Fsimilar with early rain easing to
OL,16,Fbrighter spells. Windy Monday, but
OL,17,Fdrier with sunny spells. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
